text.section:
A statement of authority shall set forth:
The name of the unincorporated nonprofit association;
The address in this Commonwealth, including the street address, if any, of the association or, if the association does not have an address in this Commonwealth, its out-of-state address;
That the association is an unincorporated nonprofit association;
The name and title or position of a person authorized to transfer an interest in real property held in the name of the association; and
An affirmation by the person executing the statement that they are duly authorized to do so.
